      "side": 1,
      "message": "ah - wait, I see. The thing being cloned is always just a variable reference in the return case. Hmm. OK, I think this is okay then? We can\u0027t quite just assert that the expression is a variable reference (it is in a few spots, but not in the out-arguments of an inlined call case), but can we actually just assert that the IsAssignable visitor succeeds?",
